  m_text: 'Select Pheromones on the left and then click the ground to place them.

    Different
    Ants will be drawn to or away from different Pheromones


    Use the Buttons
    on the Right to create new Ants. There are 3 ant types Worker/Soldier/Carpenter.


    Different
    Ant types cost different amounts of food. Make sure you are bringing in enough
    food to support all of your ants or they will die.


    Soldiers will Fight
    AntLions, Carpenters will disable Ant Traps.


    Collect all of the Rocket
    Ship Parts to help the ants get to Space.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
